From Dick Grady Subject Re Car buying story, was Christ, another dealer service scam In article LIBEMC BYUVM BITNET LIBEMC BYUVM BITNET writes Mark states in his post to know the dealer price and offer above My husband and I are in the market to buy our first car together, and neither of us know how to go about it How do you find out the dealer price Are their books to look in Do you send away somewhere for it Several company publish periodicals or times a year which list the sticker prices and the dealer invoice prices of all the cars and their options Edmund's is the name of one such price guide You can find these price guides at most places which sell magazines Dick Grady Salem, NH, USA So many newsgroups, so little time